                "text": "Ooh, I'd love to see a visualization of that output. Especially if it's not correct (232 work_days for work_hours?), it could be very funny.\n\nI worked on a bespoke IDE for hierarchical planning, which produced a timeline. This output looks like a network with weighted edges; time doesn't matter, but proportions do? Maybe there's some additional context, like the size of each bin of resource, which I can kind-of make out from the input graph. Sweet work!"
